Eliminate if Ones-Unique < 4 (aggressive)
Eliminate if Low(0–4) count NOT in [2,4]
Eliminate if not in parity majors {3E-2O, 2E-3O} (optional)
expression: not ((ones_even_count == 3 and ones_odd_count == 2) or (ones_even_count == 2 and ones_odd_count == 3))

name: Eliminate if any digit repeats ≥3 (no triples)
Eliminate if more than two distinct pairs (rare/degenerate)
expression: (sum(1 for c in Counter(combo_ones).values() if c==2) > 2)

name: Eliminate if no HOT digit present (N=5 window recommended)
expression: not any(d in hot_digits for d in combo_ones)

name: Eliminate if no DUE digit present (m=2 recommended)
expression: not any(d in due_digits for d in combo_ones)

name: Eliminate if no carryover from seed-ones (≥1 shared)
If seed ones is 2E-3O, eliminate odd-sum ones next (prefer even)
applicable_if: (sum(d % 2 == 0 for d in seed_ones) == 2 and sum(d % 2 == 1 for d in seed_ones) == 3)

name: If seed ones is 2E-3O, eliminate ones patterns not 3E-2O (aggressive)
applicable_if: (sum(d % 2 == 0 for d in seed_ones) == 2 and sum(d % 2 == 1 for d in seed_ones) == 3)

name: If seed ones is 3E-2O, eliminate ones tail patterns (1E-4O, 5E-0O)
applicable_if: (sum(d % 2 == 0 for d in seed_ones) == 3 and sum(d % 2 == 1 for d in seed_ones) == 2)

name: If seed ones is 3E-2O, eliminate ones patterns not in {3E-2O, 2E-3O} (aggressive)
applicable_if: (sum(d % 2 == 0 for d in seed_ones) == 3 and sum(d % 2 == 1 for d in seed_ones) == 2)
expression: not ((ones_even_count == 3 and ones_odd_count == 2) or (ones_even_count == 2 and ones_odd_count == 3))

name: If seed ones is 4E-1O, eliminate odd-sum ones next (prefer even)
applicable_if: (sum(d % 2 == 0 for d in seed_ones) == 4 and sum(d % 2 == 1 for d in seed_ones) == 1)

name: If seed ones is 4E-1O, eliminate ones tail patterns (1E-4O, 5E-0O)
applicable_if: (sum(d % 2 == 0 for d in seed_ones) == 4 and sum(d % 2 == 1 for d in seed_ones) == 1)

name: If seed ones is 4E-1O, eliminate ones patterns not in {3E-2O, 2E-3O} (aggressive)
applicable_if: (sum(d % 2 == 0 for d in seed_ones) == 4 and sum(d % 2 == 1 for d in seed_ones) == 1)
expression: not ((ones_even_count == 3 and ones_odd_count == 2) or (ones_even_count == 2 and ones_odd_count == 3))

name: Eliminate if Ones-Sum NOT in P10–P90 (15–29)
Eliminate if Ones-Sum NOT in P20–P80 (17–26)
Eliminate if Ones-Sum NOT in P30–P70 (19–25)
Eliminate if Ones-Sum < P10 (15)
Eliminate if Ones-Sum > P90 (29)
